<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Mameleon, located in Wijk bij Duurstede, values your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.</p>

        <p><strong>1. Personal Data We Process</strong><br>
        We may collect and process the following personal data:<br>
        - First and last name<br>
        - Email address<br>
        - Phone number<br>
        - Payment information<br>
        - Content of communications (such as emails or submitted forms)</p>

        <p><strong>2. Purpose of Processing</strong><br>
        Your personal data is used for the following purposes:<br>
        - To deliver our products and services<br>
        - Administrative and billing purposes<br>
        - To contact you regarding appointments or support<br>
        - To improve our services<br>
        - To send newsletters (only if you have subscribed)</p>

        <p><strong>3. Data Retention</strong><br>
        We retain personal data only for as long as necessary for the purpose for which it was collected, or as required by law.</p>

        <p><strong>4. Sharing With Third Parties</strong><br>
        Your data will not be shared with third parties unless it is necessary for the performance of our services or to comply with legal obligations.</p>

        <p><strong>5. Data Security</strong><br>
        Mameleon takes appropriate technical and organizational measures to secure your personal data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</p>

        <p><strong>6. Your Rights</strong><br>
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. You can contact us at the email address listed below.</p>

        <p><strong>7. Changes</strong><br>
        We reserve the right to amend this privacy policy. The latest version will always be available on our website.</p>

        <p><strong>8. Contact Information</strong><br>
        Mameleon<br>
        Wijk bij Duurstede<br>
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@mameleon.nl">info@mameleon.nl</a></p>
    </Layout>
  </body>
</html>